Flaky is a cozy home microbakery based in Zürich, lovingly baking American-style pies and treats — from buttery crusts to gooey, nostalgic flavors.

title: About
text:

Cozy spiced apples tucked under a buttery crumble.
Salted Maple Pecan Pie
Rich maple sweetness balanced with toasty pecans and a hint of salt.

title: About
text:
